'''[[predicate]] [[calculus]]''' (''[[uncountable]]'')

# {{logic}} The branch of logic that deals with [[quantified]] [[statement]]s such as "there exists an x such that..." or "for any x, it is the case that...", where x is a [[member]] of the [[domain of discourse]].

